      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.141 - Ismail ibn Jaber asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a man who trims his nails and mustache: should he wipe them with water afterward?\nImam (as) said: 'No, he is already pure.'."
